Big Endian Vs Little Endian

BIG ENDIAN (network uses it):-

(32-bit integer) 1c2c3b4d  -->  (in memory view) 1c2c3b4d

LITTLE ENDIAN (x86,ARM,etc):-

(32-bit integer) 1c2c3b4d  -->  (in memory view) 4d3b2c1c

****
ICMP Packet Structure
|Header|
<--Type-->
<--Code-->
<--Checksum-->
<--Identifier-->
<--Sequence Number-->
<--Time Stamp-->
|Data|
<Bytes>
****

**checksum of ICMP packet is created from type header till actual data(assume checksum to 0)**

